{"tid":524592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now【政情】: 立會新秩序　泛民暫緩百倍奉還","createTime":"2018-01-09T17:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T23:58:47.000Z","uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8fa8c9f1b74ecee918dd5959d4d9206e7d7198","tid":524592,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"立法會大會周三復會，新任律政司司長鄭若驊屯門寓所的僭建新鮮熱辣、民主黨林卓廷提出緊急質詢以及休會待續議案。不過，主席梁君彥認為有關事項不屬「急切」，不批准周三大會上提出，議員只可繼續場外評論。<br />\n<br />\n2017年最後一次大會在混亂中通過了議事規則修訂，泛民事後聲言會百倍奉還。經歷聖誕新年假期，是否「返來就郁」？<br />\n<br />\n修改議事規則一役的戰績仍留在議程上，包括泛民對多名建制派議員的譴責動議，以及傳召官員出席會議，當時為拉布而製造的子彈如今即使失去作用，泛民都沒有計劃要收回，否則如同退縮。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何落實百倍奉還，泛民不同板塊各有考量。溫和泛民認為修改議事規則一役反應冷淡，評估外界對他們的期望是復會而非復仇，計劃民生議題回復正常審議，待一地兩檢等議題再百倍奉還。<br />\n<br />\n真正「返來就郁」的其實是特區政府，早前因為避免成為拉布子彈，停交法案上大會近一個月。大會一復會，政府隨即提交三個法案，包括有關利得稅兩級制以及印花稅條例草案。<br />\n<br />\n印花稅條例草案去年因讓路予一地兩檢議案，政府主動提出中止審議，表示會重新審視，相隔兩個月原封不動再上會。據了解，政府接受不需申請延長換樓期的限制，即周浩鼎提出的修訂很大機會獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n2018年首次立法會大會未有百倍奉還，周浩鼎先獲光環。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=249854&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D249854%26hot%3D1&d=wlrLkrEOSxyNReAqFiqzy9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=62050d6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D249854%26hot%3D1&h=fc2faa1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=249854&amp;hot=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54279f0303672fcf4f2ab5440130c2f76a060c34","tid":524592,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/012644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F012644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aa4140cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"201f53aeedcc89a71c7056edf26a196b4dd96d9a","tid":524592,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:05:26.000Z","msg":"講就兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da33ba70aeedbaf991c1b44c7d3298e1d67b8d9f","tid":524592,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:10:36.000Z","msg":"補選投泛民啦 保住關鍵一席呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ddc35c6d7fa03bb6bb3830847daf8f954d109c","tid":524592,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:19:08.000Z","msg":"泛民打手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6848e61460af66ab181776befd0074baa76c1bdc","tid":524592,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"泛民有邊次真係還咗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedab4edb420b5290a7a4dc3cd9cbd6222ce1b4b","tid":524592,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:43:35.000Z","msg":"還到百分一偷笑啦"},{"pid":"3f1c3e5fdec64e434654c6661ede787ab63853fa","tid":524592,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補選投泛民啦 保住關鍵一席呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔投飯民就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要清蒜"}]}